#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus.oidc.proxy.proxy-configuration-name=<name>` property configures the name of proxy configuration registered in the Proxy registry (`quarkus.proxy.<name>.*`). The proxy configuration can be used to control OIDC access to HTTP proxies."
msgstr "属性 `quarkus.oidc.proxy.proxy-configuration-name=<name>` 用于配置在代理注册表（ `quarkus.proxy.<name>.*` ）中注册的代理配置名称。该代理配置可用于控制 OIDC 对 HTTP 代理的访问。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
