#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Default `TokenStateManager` keeps tokens in an encrypted session cookie by default. Encrypting the tokens increases the session cookie size - you might want to consider disabling the session cookie encryption when the Quarkus application and its clients all operate within an internal, secure network."
msgstr "默认情况下 `，TokenStateManager` 会将令牌保存在加密的会话 Cookie 中。对令牌进行加密会增加会话 Cookie 的大小——当 Quarkus 应用程序及其客户端均在内部安全网络中运行时，您可能需要考虑禁用会话 Cookie 的加密功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A session cookie encryption secret can be configured with `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-secret`. Quarkus OIDC fallbacks to the configured client secret if the encryption secret is not configured, and, if the client secret is also not available (for example, when the JWT `private_key_jwt` or MTLS client authentication method is used) -  generates a secure random secret itself. Be aware that generating an encryption secret can cause re-authentication failures in a multi-pod container deployment where one pod may not be able to decrypt a session cookie encrypted by the secret known to another pod only."
msgstr "可以通过 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-secret` 配置会话 Cookie 的加密密钥。 如果未配置加密密钥，Quarkus OIDC 将回退到配置的客户端密钥；如果客户端密钥也不可用（例如，当使用 JWT `private_key_jwt` 或 MTLS 客户端身份验证方法时），则会自行生成一个安全的随机密钥。 请注意，在多 Pod 容器部署中，生成加密密钥可能会导致重新身份验证失败，因为其中一个 Pod 可能无法解密仅由另一个 Pod 知晓的密钥所加密的会话 Cookie。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "JWE encryption is used to encrypt the session cookie, using the `A256GCMKW` algorithm to wrap the generated content encryption key by default. You can try to use the JWE `dir` encryption with `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-algorithm=dir` which can produce shorter JWE sequences as the encryption and decryption is done with the same session cookie encryption key directly, avoiding the need to generate and wrap a content encryption key."
msgstr "JWE 加密用于对会话 Cookie 进行加密，默认使用 `A256GCMKW` 算法对生成的内容加密密钥进行封装。 您可以尝试使用 JWE `目录` 加密，通过设置 ` `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-algorithm=dir` ` 来实现。由于加密和解密直接使用同一会话 Cookie 加密密钥进行，因此可以生成更短的 JWE 序列，从而无需生成和封装内容加密密钥。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The encrypted session cookie with up to three tokens may exceed a 4096 bytes cookie size limit, causing the browser to drop it. If it happens, Quarkus OIDC attempts to split the large session cookie into individual session cookie chunks by default and re-assemble them into a single session cookie when the user returns, before decrypting it. But you can try the `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.split-tokens=true` option in order to have one session cookie per token - where the main session cookie keeps an ID token, and two more session cookies - access and refresh tokens."
msgstr "包含最多三个令牌的加密会话 Cookie 可能会超过 4096 字节的 Cookie 大小限制，导致浏览器将其丢弃。如果发生这种情况，Quarkus OIDC 默认会尝试将大型会话 Cookie 拆分为多个独立的会话 Cookie 片段，并在用户返回时将其重新组合为单个会话 Cookie，然后进行解密。 但您可以尝试使用 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.split-tokens=true` 选项，以便为每个令牌分配一个会话 Cookie——其中主会话 Cookie 保存 ID 令牌，另外两个会话 Cookie 分别保存访问令牌和刷新令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.strategy` can be used to optimize the token storage by not storing the tokens your application does not intend to use."
msgstr "`quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.strategy` 可用于优化令牌存储，通过不存储应用程序无意使用的令牌来实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, you can do `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.strategy=id-refresh-tokens` which means that your application is not intending to use an access token directly or propagate it to downstream services, all it wants is to use ID token to interact with the user and keep refreshing the session."
msgstr "例如，你可以设置 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.strategy=id-refresh-tokens，` 这意味着你的应用程序并不打算直接使用访问令牌，也不会将其传递给下游服务，它仅希望使用身份令牌与用户交互并持续刷新会话。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If your application does not need to use access tokens but only interact with the authenticated user who must always re-authenticate when the session expires, consider `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.strategy=idtoken` - which retains ID token only, ignoring both access and refresh tokens."
msgstr "如果您的应用程序无需使用访问令牌，而只需与已认证的用户进行交互（该用户在会话过期时必须始终重新认证），请考虑使用 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.strategy=idtoken` —— 该策略仅保留 ID 令牌，而忽略访问令牌和刷新令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-required` and two other related properties, `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-secret` and `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-algorithm`, are also effective when custom `io.quarkus.oidc.TokenStateManager` is used, including xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#db-token-state-manager[Database TokenStateManager] and xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#redis-token-state-manager[Redis TokenStateManager]."
msgstr "`quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-required` 以及另外两个相关属性 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-secret` 和 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-algorithm，` 在使用自定义的 `io.quarkus.oidc.TokenStateManager` 时同样有效，包括 xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#db-token-state-manager[Database TokenStateManager] 和 xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#redis-token-state-manager[Redis TokenStateManager] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Given that `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-required` is set to `true` by default, a custom `io.quarkus.oidc.TokenStateManager` implementation must encrypt tokens before storing them by default. However, it does not have to encrypt tokens itself, they will be encrypted by the time it is asked to store them."
msgstr "鉴于 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-required` 默认设置为 `true，` 自定义的 `io.quarkus.oidc.TokenStateManager` 实现默认必须在存储令牌之前对其进行加密。 不过，它本身并不需要对令牌进行加密，因为在被要求存储令牌时，这些令牌已经完成了加密。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A custom `io.quarkus.oidc.TokenStateManager` implementation that does not want tokens encrypted by default can disable it with `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-required=false`."
msgstr "如果自定义的 `io.quarkus.oidc.TokenStateManager` 实现不希望默认对令牌进行加密，可以通过设置 `quarkus.oidc.token-state-manager.encryption-required=false` 来禁用此功能。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Logout"
msgstr "退出"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus OIDC supports three standard OIDC logout options: <<rp-initiated-logout>>, <<back-channel-logout>>, and <<front-channel-logout>>, as well as a local logout option. See the xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#logout-and-expiration[OIDC logout] section for more information."
msgstr "Quarkus OIDC 支持三种标准的 OIDC 注销选项： <<rp-initiated-logout>> 、 <<back-channel-logout>> 和 <<front-channel-logout>> ，以及一种本地注销选项。更多信息请参阅 xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#logout-and-expiration[“OIDC 注销] ”部分。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "RP-initiated Logout"
msgstr "由 RP 发起的注销"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`RP-initiated` logout involves the logged-in user initiating a logout request by calling an application logout endpoint. Quarkus OIDC intercepts this request, clears the session cookie and redirects the user to the OIDC provider's logout endpoint."
msgstr "`由 RP 发起的` 注销是指已登录的用户通过调用应用程序的注销端点来发起注销请求。Quarkus OIDC 会拦截此请求，清除会话 Cookie，并将用户重定向至 OIDC 提供商的注销端点。"

