#, fuzzy
msgid "You can use OIDC authentication completion actions to perform the work that must be done only once upon a successful authorization code flow completion."
msgstr "您可以使用 OIDC 身份验证完成操作，在授权码流程成功完成后执行那些只需执行一次的操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#authentication-completion-action[OIDC Authentication Completion Action] for more information."
msgstr "有关详细信息，请参阅 xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#authentication-completion-action[“OIDC 身份验证完成操作] ”。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "JavaScript request checker"
msgstr "JavaScript 请求检查器"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As described in the <<authorization-code-flow-spa>> section, Quarkus OIDC can return an error to initiate an authorization code flow for SPA\n"
"to intercept it and work around the fact that some OIDC providers do not support CORS for the authorization endpoint."
msgstr "如“ <<authorization-code-flow-spa>> ”一节所述，Quarkus OIDC 可以返回一个错误来触发授权码流程，以便 SPA 能够拦截该流程，从而规避某些 OIDC 提供商不支持授权端点的 CORS 这一问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Quarkus OIDC to do it, it needs to know if the request came from SPA. By default. it checks if the `X-Requested-With` request header with its value set to either `JavaScript` or `XMLHttpRequest` is available."
msgstr "要让 Quarkus OIDC 实现这一功能，它需要知道请求是否来自 SPA。默认情况下，它会检查请求头 `X-Requested-With` 是否存在，且其值是否为 `JavaScript` 或 `XMLHttpRequest` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See the xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#single-page-applications[Integrating with SPA] documentation for more information about customizing JavaScript request checks with custom `quarkus.oidc.JavaScriptRequestChecker` request checkers."
msgstr "有关如何使用自定义的 `quarkus.oidc.JavaScriptRequestChecker` 请求检查器来定制 JavaScript 请求检查的更多信息，请参阅《 xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#single-page-applications[与 SPA 集成] 》文档。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Local logout"
msgstr "本地注销"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The logout configuration described in the <<logout-properties>> section supports standard OIDC logout mechanism, with the Quarkus endpoint coordinating the logout process with the OIDC provider.\n"
"Sometimes, you may want to do the xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#local-logout[local logout] only to clear the local session cookie."
msgstr "“ <<logout-properties>> ”部分中描述的注销配置支持标准的 OIDC 注销机制，其中 Quarkus 端点会与 OIDC 提供商协同处理注销流程。有时，您可能只想执行 xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#local-logout[本地注销] ，以清除本地会话 Cookie。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Listen to OIDC events"
msgstr "收听 OIDC 活动"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can observe OIDC events related to the authentication, logout, etc.\n"
"See the xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#listen-to-authentication-events[Listento OIDC events] section for more information."
msgstr "您可以监听与身份验证、注销等相关的 OIDC 事件。更多信息请参阅 xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc#listen-to-authentication-events[“监听 OIDC 事件] ”一节。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Token propagation and exchange"
msgstr "代币传播与交换"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use xref:security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc#token-propagation-rest[Quarkus OIDC token propagation feature] if you need to propagate the current bearer or authorization code flow access token to the downstream service. The tokens which must be propagated can be exchanged."
msgstr "如果您需要将当前的凭证或授权码流访问令牌传递给下游服务，请使用 xref:security-openid-connect-client-reference.adoc#token-propagation-rest[Quarkus 的 OIDC 令牌传递功能] 。必须传递的令牌可以进行交换。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/security-oidc-expanded-configuration.adoc
#, fuzzy
